    <Content contentid="4134" contenttypeid="INTRO" desc="Introduction">
      <Description><![CDATA[<p>Blending exquisite design and family-friendly comforts, Villa Rodnaya is a four-bedroom holiday haven with panoramic ocean views from its hillside perch on Phuket’s idyllic northwest coast.&nbsp; Found at one of the island’s most coveted locations within Malaiwana estate at Nai Thon Beach, Rodnaya is a vibrant sanctuary complete with a children’s playroom, media room, 18-metre infinity pool and stylish indoor and outdoor living areas.&nbsp; Settle in for an indulgent stay under the care of Rodnaya’s staff team, which includes a skilled chef, and savour the tropical island life with captivating sea and sunset views from every room.</p>]]></Description>
      <SubContents />
    </Content>
    <Content contentid="4135" contenttypeid="ABTV" desc="About Villa">
      <Description><![CDATA[<p>Villa Rodnaya, a four-bedroom luxury retreat in the hills over Nai Thon Beach, is a showcase of modern design that extends a warm welcome to families and friends.&nbsp; A dazzling island escape awaits, with magical sea and sunset views over one of Phuket’s finest beaches, and a skilled team of staff to cater to your every need.</p><p>Rodnaya brings tropical holiday fantasies to life with its sparkling 18-metre pool overlooking the sea, expansive indoor and outdoor living areas, a kids’ playroom full of fun toys and games, a chic and cosy media room, and a custom-designed music studio (available on request with prior approval).&nbsp; Peace of mind for families is also assured with the added safety of a protective fence around the pool and a stair gate.</p><p>Relax in royal style under the dramatic peaked roof of the plush master bedroom suite. &nbsp; Situated in a poolside pavilion, this grand bedroom is furnished with a king-sized bed, has a double soaker tub in its ensuite bathroom, and views galore.&nbsp; The three king-bedded guest bedrooms are smaller but no less stylish with their sea-view balconies and private bathrooms.</p><p>Explore Thai cuisine and enjoy meals prepared with flair by your personal chef.&nbsp; Dine in air-conditioned grandeur at Rodnaya’s stately indoor dining room or relish the tropical breezes out on the dining terrace.&nbsp; The villa manager is on site to offer friendly assistance at the villa and help with your plans to explore the island.</p><p>Nai Thon is just nine kilometres from Phuket Airport, yet it retains the aura of an undiscovered beach with its kilometre-long stretch of soft white sand surrounded by forested parkland and a low-key village.&nbsp; Water sports include standup paddling and snorkelling, while vendors sprinkled along the beachfront sell Thai takeaway snacks and fruit.&nbsp; Phuket’s top sights and leisure activities including golf, yacht charters, beach clubs and fine dining are just a short drive away.</p>]]></Description>
      <SubContents />
    </Content>
    <Content contentid="4136" contenttypeid="LYT" desc="Layout">
      <Description><![CDATA[<p>Rodnaya is a two-storey villa arranged on the hillside in two pavilions for optimal sea and sunset views.&nbsp; Entering the villa from the car park brings you into to the top floor of the large pavilion that houses an open-plan living and dining area, guest kitchen and chef’s kitchen.&nbsp; The master suite sits in a smaller pavilion connected to the living-dining pavilion via the kids’ playroom.&nbsp; Extending across the front of the top floor is the 18-metre pool and surrounding deck with panoramic views.&nbsp; A central staircase leads down to ground floor where the three guest bedrooms, media room and music studio are situated – all with sea-view balconies.</p>]]></Description>
      <SubContents />
    </Content>
    <Content contentid="4137" contenttypeid="BDR" desc="Bed Rooms">
      <Description><![CDATA[]]></Description>
      <SubContents>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Master suite]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p>Found in its own pavilion at the edge of the pool terrace and featuring a majestic peaked ceiling, this bedroom is a romantic and private escape that will be coveted by couples.&nbsp; Relax on the four-poster king-sized bed and enjoy the superb sea views, or simply slide open the doors to be the first in the pool.&nbsp; The ensuite bathroom is elegantly appointed in white marble with a double bathtub, while its proximity to the kids’ playroom, which includes a comfortable daybed, makes it possible to create a family suite.</p>]]></Description>
          <Images />
        </SubContent>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Guest bedrooms]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p>Although these bedrooms are smaller than the master suite, each offers an ensuite bathroom and a balcony with sea views that will appeal to guests of all ages.&nbsp; All three bedrooms are furnished with king-sized beds and mirrored wardrobes.</p>]]></Description>
          <Images />
        </SubContent>
      </SubContents>
    </Content>
    <Content contentid="4138" contenttypeid="LVA" desc="Living Area">
      <Description><![CDATA[]]></Description>
      <SubContents>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Indoor living]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p>At the heart of Villa Rodnaya is an open-plan living and dining room that opens to the pool terrace; a place to gather and relax under the gorgeous arched roof.&nbsp; The living room’s soft sofas are positioned to take in the views, while the solid-wood dining table and its elegant red leather seats make every meal feel like a special occasion.&nbsp; A Bose audio system and built-in speakers both inside and out make it easy to set the mood.&nbsp; The modern guest kitchen and breakfast bar sit just behind the dining area, while the chef’s kitchen lies off to the side.</p><p>Adjacent to the living area is the colourful kids’ playroom with a good assortment of toys and games, while the media room downstairs offers more entertainment choices.&nbsp; A custom-designed recording studio is available for hire by guests for an additional fee and on approval from the villa owner.</p> ]]></Description>
          <Images />
        </SubContent>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Outdoor living]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p>With its 18-metre pearl-toned marble pool and spectacular sea views, Villa Rodnaya’s terrace is a photo-perfect spot.&nbsp; The pool is protected by a fence of transparent panels that keeps toddlers safe while not obstructing the tropical views.&nbsp; Enjoy alfresco meals in the shade of the poolside dining <span style="font-style: italic;">sala </span>or soak up the sun on one of the sunbeds that line the pool.</p>]]></Description>
          <Images />
        </SubContent>
      </SubContents>
    </Content>
